<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 14:07:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>自10月7日以来，以色列特种部队解救了哈马斯在加沙扣押的四名人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-forces-rescue-four-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018f-f78b-d660-af9f-ffbfb2190000</link><description>获救人质诺亚·阿加马尼 (Noa Argamani)、阿尔莫格·梅厄 (Almog Meir)、安德烈·科兹洛夫 (Andrey Kozlov) 和什洛米·齐夫 (Shlomi Ziv) 于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架，并在以色列的一次行动中获救，行动之前进行了数周的情报收集</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 11:33:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-forces-rescue-four-israeli-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018f-f78b-d660-af9f-ffbfb2190000</guid></item><item><title>定居者将这个巴勒斯坦家庭驱逐出村庄。然后恐怖又开始了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-expelled-them-from-their-village-then-the-terror-began-all-over-again-again/0000018f-f67e-d84e-adbf-f77f421e0000</link><description>由于害怕定居者，一个巴勒斯坦牧羊家庭在战争开始后逃离了南希伯伦山的村庄。他们带着羊群搬迁，但在新的避难所却找不到任何缓解。上周，一名年轻男子遭到武装蒙面定居者袭击后入院治疗</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/settlers-expelled-them-from-their-village-then-the-terror-began-all-over-again-again/0000018f-f67e-d84e-adbf-f77f421e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国库已成为极端正统学校系统的ATM机，助长腐败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.highlight/israels-treasury-has-become-the-haredi-school-systems-atm-encouraging-corruption/0000018f-f50f-df2e-a5df-f77ff10c0000</link><description>如果它承担了极端正统教育网络所欠下的大部分债务，财政部将向其发出信号，疏忽是没有代价的</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 06:13:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article/.highlight/israels-treasury-has-become-the-haredi-school-systems-atm-encouraging-corruption/0000018f-f50f-df2e-a5df-f77ff10c0000</guid></item><item><title>特种部队军官在加沙解救人质行动中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</link><description>战时内阁部长甘茨在人质获释后推迟周六发表声明 ■ 以色列国防军表示，部队对加沙中部代尔巴拉赫和努塞拉特地区的哈马斯目标进行了大规模袭击 ■ 以色列表示，在加沙南部的 Al-Mawasi 建立了第 11 所野战医院 ■ 22-约旦河西岸图勒凯尔姆附近一岁巴勒斯坦人被以色列国防军炮火打死 ■ 以色列国防军加强对加沙美国临时浮动码头的安全保卫 ■ 也门胡塞武装在突然镇压中拘留了 11 名联合国工作人员和援助人员</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 03:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-live/idf-drone-fired-from-lebanon-fell-in-open-area-in-north-after-failed-interception-attempt/0000018f-f5d1-d190-af8f-fff30f860000</guid></item><item><title>“你支持恐怖主义”：10 月 7 日事件后，犹太学校的以色列阿拉伯教师面临迫害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</link><description>尽管与以色列社会有疏离感，并且在某些情况下，个人安全感下降，但犹太教育系统中的阿拉伯教师仍然相信自己有使命要完成</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 23:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-arab-teachers-in-jewish-schools-face-persecution-in-wake-of-oct-7/0000018f-f4d7-d84e-adbf-f5df0fe90000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日，哈马斯想要唤起大屠杀”：诺贝尔奖获得者作家赫塔·穆勒的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-wanted-to-evoke-the-shoah-an-interview-with-nobel-winning-author-herta-muller/0000018f-edf4-d3f3-a7ff-fff482590000</link><description>诺贝尔文学奖获得者赫塔·穆勒从未试图隐瞒家族的纳粹历史，也从未试图逃避她生活在独裁统治下的岁月。事实上，她利用自己的过去来表达对现在的批评以及对以色列未来的担忧</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 22:32:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-08/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/hamas-wanted-to-evoke-the-shoah-an-interview-with-nobel-winning-author-herta-muller/0000018f-edf4-d3f3-a7ff-fff482590000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列打击真主党，伊朗也会加入。那么美国就会被拖进去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/the-danger-of-israels-unwillingness-to-see-gaza-and-lebanon-as-communicating-vessels/0000018f-f2be-df2e-a5df-f6ff23480000</link><description>以色列不仅拒绝了华盛顿的“通讯船”理论，还为攻击真主党作为防御举措建立了一个合乎逻辑但危险且鲁莽的理由</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 19:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/the-danger-of-israels-unwillingness-to-see-gaza-and-lebanon-as-communicating-vessels/0000018f-f2be-df2e-a5df-f6ff23480000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的军事审查似乎是在保护内塔尼亚胡，而不是国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-military-censor-seems-to-be-protecting-netanyahu-not-national-security/0000018f-f381-d084-abef-f7c96c420000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 17:53:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-06-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-military-censor-seems-to-be-protecting-netanyahu-not-national-security/0000018f-f381-d084-abef-f7c96c420000</guid></item><item><title>联合国将以色列和哈马斯列入加沙战争期间伤害冲突地区儿童的国家“黑名单”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/un-adds-israel-to-blacklist-of-countries-that-harm-children-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-f37e-d084-abef-f77f242f0000</link><description>虽然将以色列列入名单并不立即构成制裁的理由，但人们担心这最终会导致针对该国的决定。一位外交消息人士告诉路透社，哈马斯和巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战组织也将被列入联合国黑名单</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:51:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/un-adds-israel-to-blacklist-of-countries-that-harm-children-amid-gaza-war/0000018f-f37e-d084-abef-f77f242f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 245 天：据报道卡塔尔威胁驱逐哈马斯领导人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-245-qatar-reportedly-threatens-to-deport-hamas-leaders/0000018f-f312-d630-a7af-fbbafa8e0000</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，卡塔尔威胁称，如果哈马斯拒绝当前停火提议，将驱逐哈马斯领导人 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府表示，任命一个国家调查委员会对 10 月 7 日进行调查的“时机尚未成熟” ■ 战时内阁部长甘茨将宣布辞职内塔尼亚胡政府于周六晚发表的讲话 ■ 战争进入 245 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-245-qatar-reportedly-threatens-to-deport-hamas-leaders/0000018f-f312-d630-a7af-fbbafa8e0000</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，随着战争死亡人数上升，加沙妇女和儿童被杀的频率减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/women-and-children-of-gaza-are-killed-less-frequently-as-wars-toll-rises-data-shows/0000018f-f343-d190-af8f-fff3b4420000</link><description>美联社对加沙卫生部数据的审查显示，以色列与哈马斯战争中死亡的巴勒斯坦妇女和儿童人数似乎已大幅下降，因为以色列因加沙空前的平民伤亡而受到国际社会的强烈批评</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 16:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/women-and-children-of-gaza-are-killed-less-frequently-as-wars-toll-rises-data-shows/0000018f-f343-d190-af8f-fff3b4420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列甘茨预计将于周六宣布从内塔尼亚胡政府辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/benny-gantz-expected-to-announce-resignation-from-the-government-on-saturday/0000018f-f2f2-d190-af8f-fff2b6b90000</link><description>甘茨几周前宣布，他打算退出内塔尼亚胡领导的政府，除非加沙战后治理计划在 6 月 8 日之前获得批准。他还希望在发出最后通牒时，人质协议谈判能够取得进展过期</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 14:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/benny-gantz-expected-to-announce-resignation-from-the-government-on-saturday/0000018f-f2f2-d190-af8f-fff2b6b90000</guid></item><item><title>“每个人都伤痕累累”：美国犹太夏令营如何准备与众不同的一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-u-s-jewish-summer-camps-are-preparing-for-a-year-like-no-other/0000018f-edca-d5c6-a1cf-fdde30550000</link><description>随着以色列-加沙战争进入第九个月，数万名美国犹太孩子即将前往夏令营。三名阵营负责人告诉《国土报》，他们已准备好应对这一前所未有的挑战</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 14:12:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-u-s-jewish-summer-camps-are-preparing-for-a-year-like-no-other/0000018f-edca-d5c6-a1cf-fdde30550000</guid></item><item><title>居民想要离开，预备役军人从未想过他们会回来——穿越以色列废弃北部的旅程</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-journey-across-israels-abandoned-north/0000018f-f276-d3f3-a7ff-f27678760000</link><description>真主党的弹幕之间，只有加利利的军事哨所已经满员，压倒性的情绪是一种绝望</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 13:22:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-journey-across-israels-abandoned-north/0000018f-f276-d3f3-a7ff-f27678760000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫最阴沉的骄傲活动让加沙人质成为焦点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-avivs-most-somber-pride-event-put-gaza-hostages-center-stage/0000018f-f18a-d55d-a39f-fd8e280e0000</link><description>随着加沙战争愈演愈烈，另一项停火和人质协议似乎还很遥远，特拉维夫这个以一年一度的骄傲游行而闻名的城市，今年的活动专门关注人质家属的困境，强化了他们与亲人见面的要求。那些返回</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 09:27:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tel-avivs-most-somber-pride-event-put-gaza-hostages-center-stage/0000018f-f18a-d55d-a39f-fd8e280e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府回应总检察长：10月7日成立调查委员会时机尚不成熟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/ag-urges-netanyahu-to-set-up-commission-of-inquiry-into-gaza-war-to-counter-backlash/0000018f-f170-dbca-a99f-fbf609770000</link><description>总检察长的信警告内塔尼亚胡，逃避对以色列在加沙行动的适当调查可能会导致“国家利益”受到“重大损害”，因为该国在国际法庭上面临挑战</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 08:02:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/ag-urges-netanyahu-to-set-up-commission-of-inquiry-into-gaza-war-to-counter-backlash/0000018f-f170-dbca-a99f-fbf609770000</guid></item><item><title>“一旦我离开以色列国防军，我就感到自己微不足道。一周后我被征召去执行预备役任务”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：两个朋友正在规划他们的退伍生活，一位音乐家和舞蹈家解释了为什么跟随比领导更有意义</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-07/ty-article/.highlight/once-i-left-the-idf-i-felt-insignificant-a-week-later-i-was-called-up-for-reserve-duty/0000018f-f0af-dbca-a99f-fbff27ee0000</guid></item><item><title>全球对以色列的经济抵制获得关注，但政府没有答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</link><description>世界正在对以色列在加沙战争中的行为失去耐心并采取措施——限制出口、取消专业会议、放弃计划中的商业交易等等。当地消费者将遭受损失</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:09:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-global-economic-boycott-of-israel-gains-traction-but-the-government-has-no-answers/0000018f-efc2-df2e-a5df-eff711a20000</guid></item><item><title>国际合法性的减弱、疲惫不堪的军队和黎巴嫩战争将把以色列推向边缘</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</link><description>与真主党的战争将成为以色列后方的重大挑战：北部和中部的城市将面临前所未有的规模和火力威胁。 在加沙，哈马斯和以色列国防军之间的版本之战仍在继续，而且缺乏明确的信息目标正在影响疲惫的士兵 ■ 对于悲惨的以色列国防军首领赫茨尔·哈勒维来说，时间已经不多了</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:01:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/waning-intl-legitimacy-an-exhausted-army-and-war-in-lebanon-will-push-israel-to-the-edge/0000018f-ef1b-d3f3-a7ff-ff3b7db00000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡使用并虐待了甘茨和艾森科特——但当他们离开后，他会想念他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</link><description>如果民族团结党兑现其巩固内塔尼亚胡联盟的威胁，他将失去保护他免受国外更大批评的防弹衣。 ■ 当总理在美国国会发表讲话时，他将重复他在 2015 年所进行的赌博 –并希望有不同的结果</description><pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-used-and-abused-gantz-and-eisenkot-but-hell-miss-them-when-theyre-gone/0000018f-ef1d-dff6-a9df-ef9f9adb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>